{"id":"6455","user":{"id":"314171","nickname":"假编程猫258","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMzE0MTcxXzMxNDE3MV8xNjU4Mzg4OTczNzc3XzMzMDRiYTk5.png","subject_id":211,"work_shop_name":"跃动工作室","work_shop_level":3,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【教程】制作属于自己的课件","content":"<p>大家好，这里是五百年没更新教程的假编猫</p>\n<p>今天我不教IDE，教制作课件！</p>\n<p>（众：快讲啊！）</p>\n<p>好吧······</p>\n<p>----------------------------------------------分界线--------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<p>首先开启电脑</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fqu3H91elGSh2Jiw-uPzQ6jyLBef\"><br></p>\n<p>好吧我电脑有点老旧，课件也很多······</p>\n<p>话不多说，我们单击右键，把鼠标移到新建上，新建一个演示文稿：<br><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fr8JsMnfu76ev9ZfJs8_IjDGrSzP\"><br></p>\n<p>看到方框了吗？我们点进去（没办法演示右键新建演示文稿）</p>\n<p>点进去是会看到这样的场面：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FnPbi0iYGaYQgPvNeJ5IuWM_HyBx\"><br></p>\n<p>07的也没事，反正就是这样，要单击添加幻灯片的直接点击。首先设置版式：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FlDJW4LZq5oTVRmGGtLehgL8N1mF\"><br></p>\n<p>单击被红框框起来的地方就行了。</p>\n<p>设置底色：</p>\n<p>单击格式，单击幻灯片设计，就能设底色</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FsBiZVXbmyhcFcLcai_O9WpLErVl\"><br></p>\n<p>背景自己选，下面添加动画：</p>\n<p>单击幻灯片放映，单击动画方案：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FpDXECLRAZ993wr1FucZhLtsDuSn\"><br></p>\n<p>点这个之后会出现这种场面，动画自己选啦！</p>\n<p>好了今天教程就到这里了，谢谢！</p>\n<p><br></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1510910864,"created_at":1505620307,"n_views":213,"n_replies":21,"n_comments":1,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}